Source: tokentube
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Juergen Pabel <juergen@pabel.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), po-debconf, autotools-dev, libscrypt-dev, libgcrypt20-dev, libgpgme11-dev, libgpg-error-dev, libpam0g-dev, e2fslibs-dev, libconfuse-dev, libesmtp-dev, libpython3.4-dev, liblua5.2-dev, libplymouth-dev, libglib2.0-dev, libgtk-3-dev, liblightdm-gobject-1-dev, libcurl4-openssl-dev
