Package: tokentube
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, cryptsetup, openssl, libconfuse0, python3.4
Description: integration component between LUKS/dm-crypt and PAM
 It allows for username based logins at the Pre-Boot-Authentication screen for
 encrypted systems. An optional component allows for automatic credential passing
 to GNOME/KDE desktops for automatic logins.

Package: tokentube-ssod
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, tokentube
Description: TokenTube Single-Sign-On daemon
 Tokentube Pre-Boot-Authentication SSO daemon for pass-through to login manager

Package: tokentube-sso-lightdm
Section: x11
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, tokentube-ssod, lightdm, liblightdm-gobject-1-0
Description: TokenTube Single-Sign-On for LightDM
 Tokentube Pre-Boot-Authentication SSO pass-through to LightDM Window-Manager

Package: tokentube-plugin-python
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, tokentube, libpython3.4
Description: PYTHON plugin for TokenTube
 Plugins allow for implementing custom functionality using PYTHON

Package: tokentube-plugin-lua
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, tokentube, liblua5.2-0
Description: LUA plugin for TokenTube
 Plugins allow for implementing custom functionality using LUA

Package: tokentube-plugin-misc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, tokentube
Description: Test plugins for TokenTube (for unit-tests and such, almost a development package)
 The packaged plugin 'test' implements mostly storage related APIs so that files are stored 
 in subdirectories of the current directory. Mostly useful for unit-tests and such. The other
 plugins are demo plugins that log events.

Package: tokentube-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: tokentube (= ${binary:Version}), libc6-dev | libc-dev
Description: Development package for tokentube
 Not yet implemented

Package: tokentube-udeb
Section: debian-installer
XC-Package-Type: udeb
Architecture: any
Depends: cryptsetup-udeb
Description: Debian-Installer package for TokenTube
 Not yet implemented
